      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Not so sure about this from a design perspective. We've kind of been here. We switched forth and back between mutable and non-mutable parameters in chainparams.cpp:\n- a25fd6be138ff2bff7e2ad6a1a789db523c0193f (#4845) introduced CModifiableParams\n- 59bd89f11636e90b2d684e8f411d8d7a88622458 (#5871) removed them again\n\nThis does the same, in yet another way.\nBack then we decided we didn't actually need modifyable parameters for testing.\n\nDid that change again?\n",
